content.webTitle: Honk if you support Corbyn: have you been following the election this week?

fields.headline: Honk if you support Corbyn: have you been following the election this week?
fields.bodyText: It’s the Guardian weekly politics quiz. Not about policy announcements or polling numbers or productivity figures, but about how much you can remember of the WTF moments from the last seven days of general election campaigning. No prizes. Just for fun. Let us know how you get on in the comments … The Guardian weekly politics quiz
